         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Harbechis son of Ergeus to Apollonios and Herakleides, sitologoi for the granary at Theogonis. I acknowledge that I have received from you from the store in your hands the loan of fifteen artabas of wheat, total 15 artabas of wheat, by the 6-choinix measure of Kerkeosiris, which amount I will measure out to you by Payni 30, and if I fail to do so I will measure half as much again. The 54th year, Payni 18.</ab>
